</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,981,151,214]" box="[151,981,187,214]" pageId="4" pageNumber="225">
(Males of 
<taxonomicName box="[266,446,187,213]" class="Arachnida" family="Assamiidae" genus="Filopalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Opiliones" pageId="4" pageNumber="225" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="altomontanus" status="sp. nov.">
